OL,3,CJury told not to speculate on absence
OL,4,Cof Rochdale grooming trial defendant
OL,6,FThe jury in the trial of seven Asian
OL,7,Fmen accused of treating two teenage
OL,8,Fgirls in Rochdale as "sex slaves" have
OL,9,Fbeen told "not to speculate" why one
OL,10,Fof them is not in the dock.
OL,12,FThe prosecution allege that the
OL,13,Fcomplainants were groomed from the age
OL,14,Fof 13 to have sex with the men
OL,15,F"whenever and wherever they wanted",
OL,16,Fbetween 2001 and 2006.
OL,18,FThe defendants all deny various sexual
OL,19,Foffence, including rape and indecent
OL,20,Fassault.
