OL,3,CJury told not to speculate on absence
OL,4,Cof Rochdale grooming trial defendant
OL,6,FOne of the accused, Kasir Bashir, 50,
OL,7,Fhas not attended the trial at
OL,8,FManchester Minshull Street Crown Court.
OL,10,FIt is alleged the former stallholder
OL,11,Fon Rochdale Market raped one of the
OL,12,Fcomplainants, Girl B, on multiple
OL,13,Foccasions at a house in Chadderton,
OL,14,FOldham, along with several others.
OL,16,FBashir, of Napier Street East, Oldham,
OL,17,Fhas pleaded not guilty to two counts
OL,18,Fof rape and two counts of indecency
OL,19,Fwith a child.
